shared_text:
North Putnam High School
November 8, 2019 at 6:17 PM 路

Our outside athletic facility is beginning to take shape with many of the deep underground utilities being roughed in this week. Next week footers will be started, and before you know, we will have walls! This facility opens up inside classroom spaces and helps with safety and security at evening activities. This building will house four outside locker rooms, public bathrooms and be the new home for concessions for all outside facilities. We are excited to see this progress and look forward to opening this building!
text:
North Putnam High School
November 8, 2019 at 6:17 PM 路

Our outside athletic facility is beginning to take shape with many of the deep underground utilities being roughed in this week. Next week footers will be started, and before you know, we will have walls! This facility opens up inside classroom spaces and helps with safety and security at evening activities. This building will house four outside locker rooms, public bathrooms and be the new home for concessions for all outside facilities. We are excited to see this progress and look forward to opening this building!

post_text:
This morning Bus 22 was rear ended westbound on SR 36 near Groveland. Our transportation and security personnel responded to the scene. All students were transported to a local medical facility as a precautionary measure for evaluation. The students and bus driver were evaluated and released to parents or brought to school on a different bus. To our knowledge, no one was admitted for care.

We thank the staff who reported to the hospital to assist our students. We thank Hendricks Regional Health for their prompt and professional response today. And, thank you to all who remained in buildings and assisted in covering the school site.
